#

Pecan-Crusted Pork Tenderloin with Sweet Potato Mash

$25.99
620 kcal

Allergens:

Nuts

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

Main CourseAmerican CuisineComfort Food

Description

A succulent pork tenderloin crusted with pecans, served alongside creamy sweet potato mash for a delightful balance of flavors.

Ingredients

  • Pork Tenderloin: 1 lb
  • Pecans: 1 cup, chopped
  • Sweet Potatoes: 2 medium
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Maple Syrup: 2 tbsp
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Fresh Thyme: 1 tsp
